  - ID: 100012
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uC5D0\uC774\uD504\uB9B4"
    name_EN: April
    Text_KR: "\uD6C4\uC544!"
    Text_EN: Phew.
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400021
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 1
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100013
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC5B4\uB54C? \uB3D9\uD654\uCC98\uB7FC \uC0B4\uC558\uC9C0?"
    Text_EN: How was it? You survived just like in a fairy tale, right?!
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400021
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 3
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100014
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uC5D0\uC774\uD504\uB9B4"
    name_EN: April
    Text_KR: "\uADF8\uAC74 \uB0B4\uAC00 \uB5A8\uC5B4\uC9C8 \uB54C \uB9C8\uBC95\uC744
      \uAC78\uC5C8\uAE30 \uB54C\uBB38\uC774\uC796\uC544, \uB798\uB9AC..."
    Text_EN: That's only because I cast a spell when I was falling, Rary...
    portrait1: 400016
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400021
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 1
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100015
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uD5E4\uD5E4."
    Text_EN: Hehe!
    portrait1: 400016
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400021
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 3
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100016
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uB124\uAC00 \uB9C8\uBC95\uC744 \uAC78\uC9C0 \uC54A\uC558\uB354\uB77C\uBA74
      \uB0B4\uAC00 \uAC78\uC5C8\uC744 \uD14C\uB2C8 \uAD1C\uCC2E\uC544!"
    Text_EN: Even if you hadn't, I would have cast one, so it's totally fine!
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 3
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100017
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uB2E4\uB9CC... \uBB38\uC81C\uAC00 \uC788\uC5B4. "
    Text_EN: Except... we actually have a problem.
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 3
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100018
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uC5D0\uC774\uD504\uB9B4"
    name_EN: April
    Text_KR: "\uBB54\uB370?"
    Text_EN: What is it?
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 1
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100019
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC808\uBCBD \uC544\uB798\uC5D0\uB3C4 \uBC84\uC12F\uBB34\uB9AC\uAC00
      \uC788\uC5C8\uC5B4."
    Text_EN: There was a whole patch of mushrooms right below the cliff, too.
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 3
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100020
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uC5D0\uC774\uD504\uB9B4"
    name_EN: April
    Text_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC..."
    Text_EN: Rary...
    portrait1: 400016
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 1
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100021
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uAD1C\uCC2E\uC544! \uC774\uBC88\uC5D4 \uC6B0\uB9AC\uAC00 \uD574\uACB0\uD560
      \uC218 \uC788\uC744 \uAC70\uC57C."
    Text_EN: Don't worry! We can definitely handle it this time!
    portrait1: 400016
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 3
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100022
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC0AC\uB78C\uB4E4\uC758 \uC2DC\uC120\uC5D0\uC11C \uBC97\uC5B4\uB0AC\uC73C\uB2C8\uAE4C."
    Text_EN: We're completely out of people's sight, anyway.
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 3
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100023
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uC5D0\uC774\uD504\uB9B4"
    name_EN: April
    Text_KR: "\uD6C4, \uADF8\uB7FC \uD798\uC744 \uC368\uB3C4 \uB41C\uB2E4\uB294 \uAC70\uC9C0?"
    Text_EN: Sigh. So, does that mean I can use my power now?
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 1
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100024
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uD3B8\uD558\uAC8C \uC368. \uB9C8\uBC95 \uC4F0\uB294 \uBC95\uC740 \uC78A\uC9C0
      \uC54A\uC558\uC9C0?"
    Text_EN: Use it freely! You haven't forgotten how to use magic, right?
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 1
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100025
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uC5D0\uC774\uD504\uB9B4"
    name_EN: April
    Text_KR: "\uB2F9\uC5F0\uD558\uC9C0, \uB9C8\uBC95\uC758 \uCC45\uC7A5\uC5D0 \uAC19\uC740
      \uC885\uB958\uC758 \uCC45 3\uAD8C\uC744 \uC815\uB82C\uD558\uBA74 \uADF8 \uCC45\uC758
      \uB9C8\uBC95\uC774 \uBC1C\uB3D9\uD558\uB294\uAC70\uC796\uC544?"
    Text_EN: Obviously. If I line up three books of the same kind in the magic bookshelf,
      that book's spell activates.
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 1
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100026
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC815\uD655\uD574! \uADF8\uB7EC\uBA74 \uC138 \uBC88 \uC815\uB82C\uD574\uC11C
      \uBAAC\uC2A4\uD130\uB97C \uC81C\uC555\uD574\uBCF4\uC790!"
    Text_EN: Exactly! Let's line them up three times and take down the monsters!
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 1
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100027
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC798\uD558\uACE0 \uC788\uC5B4, \uC5D0\uC774\uD504\uB9B4! "
    Text_EN: You're doing great, April!
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 3
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100028
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uC5D0\uC774\uD504\uB9B4"
    name_EN: April
    Text_KR: "\uC774\uB807\uAC8C \uCC45 \uC815\uB82C\uC5D0 \uD55C \uBC88 \uC131\uACF5\uD560
      \uB54C\uB9C8\uB2E4 \uCF64\uBCF4 \uD69F\uC218\uAC00 \uC313\uC774\uACE0,"
    Text_EN: And every time I successfully align colors like this, my combo count
      builds up...
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 1
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100029
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uBAAC\uC2A4\uD130\uB97C \uCC98\uCE58\uD560 \uB54C\uB9C8\uB2E4 \uACBD\uD5D8\uCE58\uB97C
      \uC5BB\uC744 \uC218\uB3C4 \uC788\uC9C0!"
    Text_EN: Plus, you get EXP every time you defeat a monster!
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 3
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100030
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uACBD\uD5D8\uCE58\uB97C \uCC44\uC6E0\uC73C\uB2C8 \uC131\uC7A5\uC744
      \uD560 \uB54C\uB124!"
    Text_EN: You've filled up your EXP bar, so it's time to grow!
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 3
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100031
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uB808\uBCA8\uC5C5\uC744 \uD558\uBA74 \uC778\uCC48\uD2B8\uB97C \uC120\uD0DD\uD560
      \uC218 \uC788\uB2E4\uACE0 \uB9D0\uD574\uC92C\uC5C8\uC9C0?"
    Text_EN: I told you that you get to choose an Enchantment when you level up,
      right?
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 3
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100032
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC778\uCC48\uD2B8\uB294 \uC6B0\uB9AC\uC758 \uC2A4\uD0AC\uACFC \uACF5\uACA9\uC744
      \uAC15\uD654\uD574\uC8FC\uB294 \uD798\uC774\uC57C."
    Text_EN: Enchantments are the awesome power that boosts our skills and attacks!
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 3
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100033
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uB3D9\uD654 \uC18D\uC5D0\uC11C\uB9CC \uC720\uC9C0\uB41C\uB2E4\uB294
      \uAC8C \uC544\uC26C\uC6B4 \uC810\uC774\uC9C0\uB9CC,"
    Text_EN: It's a bummer they only work inside the fairy tale world, but...
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400020
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 3
    BG: 20001
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100034
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uADF8\uB7FC \uC2A4\uD0AC\uC744 \uC124\uBA85\uD574 \uC904\uAC8C."
    Text_EN: Let me explain the skills for you!
    portrait1: 0
    direction1: 0
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 0
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 0
    BG: 0
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100035
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC790\uB3D9 \uACF5\uACA9 \uC2A4\uD0AC\uC744 \uD68D\uB4DD\uD558\uBA74
      \uACF5\uACA9\uC18D\uB3C4\uC5D0 \uBE44\uB840\uD574 \uACF5\uACA9\uD560 \uC218
      \uC788\uAC8C \uB418\uACE0, \uC790\uB3D9 \uACF5\uACA9 \uD69F\uC218\uC5D0 \uB530\uB77C
      \uC2A4\uD0AC\uC744 \uBC1C\uB3D9\uD560 \uC218 \uC788\uC5B4"
    Text_EN: When you get the Auto-Attack skill, you can attack based on your attack
      speed, and skills will activate depending on your total auto-attacks.
    portrait1: 0
    direction1: 0
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 0
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 0
    BG: 0
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100036
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC989, \uC774 \uC2A4\uD0AC\uC740 \uC790\uB3D9 \uACF5\uACA9\uC774 \uCD1D
      15\uBC88 \uB098\uAC00\uC57C \uBC1C\uB3D9\uB420 \uC218 \uC788\uB294 \uAC70\uC9C0."
    Text_EN: So, this specific skill activates after a total of 15 auto-attacks go
      out.
    portrait1: 0
    direction1: 0
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 0
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 0
    BG: 0
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100037
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC870\uD569 \uC2A4\uD0AC\uC740 \uC815\uD574\uC9C4 \uC870\uD569\uC758
      \uCC45 3\uAD8C\uC744 \uC21C\uC11C\uC640 \uC0C1\uAD00 \uC5C6\uC774 \uC815\uB82C\uD558\uBA74
      \uBC1C\uB3D9\uD560 \uC218 \uC788\uC5B4"
    Text_EN: Combination skills trigger when you line up three specific colored books,
      regardless of the order!
    portrait1: 0
    direction1: 0
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 0
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 0
    BG: 0
    CG: 0
    BGM: 0
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100038
    GroupID: 3002
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC774 \uC2A4\uD0AC\uC740 \uBE68\uAC04\uC0C9 \uCC45, \uB178\uB780\uC0C9
