    GroupID: 3003
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uC5D0\uC774\uD504\uB9B4"
    name_EN: April
    Text_KR: "\uC5EC\uAE30\uAC00 \uC815\uB9D0 \uB3D9\uD654 \uC18D\uC758 \uC138\uACC4\uC57C?"
    Text_EN: Is this really... a world inside a fairy tale?
