  - ID: 100115
    GroupID: 3003
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uBB50\uC57C, \uC544\uC9C1 \uC548 \uBBFF\uACE0 \uC788\uC5C8\uAD6C\uB098?"
    Text_EN: What?! Oh my gosh, you mean you still didn't believe me until now?!
