    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100116
    GroupID: 3003
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uD558\uAE34, \uB2E4\uB978 \uACF3\uC5D0\uC120 \uC774\uB7F0 \uB9C8\uBC95\uC740
      \uBCFC \uC218 \uC5C6\uC5C8\uC744\uD14C\uB2C8\uAE4C!"
    Text_EN: True, true! After all, a spectacular magic like this is something you'd
      never ever find in any other corner of the world!
