    name_EN: April
    Text_KR: "\uC5B4\uB5A4 \uD0D0\uC0AC\uB300\uC600\uB098\uC694? \uC800\uB294 \uC804\uD600
      \uBAB0\uB77C\uC11C..."
    Text_EN: what kind of expeditionary force was it? I don't know anything about
      it...
