    GroupID: 3007
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC870\uC218\uB85C \uBC1B\uC740\uC9C0 \uC5BC\uB9C8 \uC548\uB410\uAC70\uB4E0. "
    Text_EN: Well, you see, I only took them in as my assistant a little while ago!
