  - ID: 100272
    GroupID: 3007
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uB300\uC2E0 \uC544\uD2C0\uB780\uC744 \uAC00\uC7A5 \uBA3C\uC800 \uB370\uB824\uC654\uC73C\uB2C8,
      \uC774\uD574\uD574\uC918. "
    Text_EN: Come on, give me a break! I made sure to bring Atlan to you before anyone
