  - ID: 100339
    GroupID: 3010
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uB3C4\uCC29\uD55C \uC138\uACC4\uC758 \uC8FC\uC778\uACF5\uC774 \uB418\uC9C0
      \uB9D0 \uAC83."
    Text_EN: Never become the protagonist of the world you arrive in.
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 400020
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 0
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 2
    BG: 20011
    CG: 0
    BGM: 2002
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100340
    GroupID: 3010
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uB3D9\uD654\uC758 \uC8FC\uC778\uACF5\uC774 \uBC14\uB00C\uBA74, \uC138\uACC4\uAC00
      \uBB34\uB108\uC9C8 \uC218\uB3C4 \uC788\uC5B4. "
    Text_EN: If the protagonist of the story gets replaced, that entire world might
      just crumble to pieces.
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 400020
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 0
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 2
    BG: 20011
    CG: 0
    BGM: 2002
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100341
    GroupID: 3010
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uD070 \uC601\uD5A5\uC744 \uC8FC\uC9C0 \uC54A\uB294 \uC870\uC5F0 \uC815\uB3C4\uB294
      \uAD1C\uCC2E\uC9C0\uB9CC, \uD750\uB984\uC744 \uBC14\uAFC0 \uC815\uB3C4\uC758
      \uC601\uD5A5\uB825\uC744 \uB07C\uCE58\uBA74 \uC548\uB3FC. "
    Text_EN: Playing a minor role that doesn't change much is totally fine, but we
      must never exert enough influence to shift the entire course of events.
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 400020
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 0
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 2
    BG: 20011
    CG: 0
    BGM: 2002
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100342
    GroupID: 3010
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC774 \uC138\uACC4\uC758 \uACBD\uC6B0\uC5D0\uB294 \uC870\uAE08 \uD2B9\uC218\uD55C
      \uC0C1\uD669\uC774\uC5C8\uB358 \uAC83 \uBFD0\uC774\uC57C."
