    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100625
    GroupID: 3017
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC5D0\uC624\uD504\uB294 \uC6D0\uB798 \uB9C8\uBB3C\uC744 \uC7A1\uC544\uC11C
      \uBD80\uC0B0\uBB3C\uC744 \uD314\uC544\uC11C \uBA39\uACE0 \uC0B4\uB358 \uB3C4\uC2DC\uC600\uC5B4. "
    Text_EN: So, you see, Aeop was originally a city that made a living by hunting
      down monsters and selling their loot!
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 400020
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400060
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 2
    BG: 20035
    CG: 0
    BGM: 2007
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100626
    GroupID: 3017
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uADF8\uB798\uC11C \uB9C8\uBC95\uC0AC\uAC00 \uB9CE\uC558\uACE0."
    Text_EN: That's why there were so many wizards around.
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 400020
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400060
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 2
    BG: 20035
