    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100627
    GroupID: 3017
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uB2E4\uB9CC \uC804\uD22C\uB97C \uC704\uD55C \uB9C8\uBC95\uC744 \uB2E4\uB8E8\uB294
      \uB9C8\uBC95\uC0AC\uAC00 \uC555\uB3C4\uC801\uC73C\uB85C \uB9CE\uC558\uC9C0. "
    Text_EN: Except, the vast majority of them specialized in combat magic.
    portrait1: 400010
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 400020
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400060
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 2
    BG: 20035
    CG: 0
    BGM: 2007
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 100628
    GroupID: 3017
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uADF8\uB798\uC11C \uADF8 \uB9C8\uBC95\uC0AC\uC758 \uC758\uACAC\uC774
      \uC9C0\uC9C0 \uBC1B\uC9C0 \uBABB\uD588\uB358 \uAC83\uB3C4 \uC788\uC5C8\uB358\uAC70\uC57C. "
    Text_EN: And that's exactly why that wizard's idea couldn't get any backing back
