  - ID: 100938
    GroupID: 3023
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC774 \uC232\uC758 \uC808\uBCBD \uB05D\uC5D0\uB294 \uC2E0\uBE44\uD55C
      \uD604\uC0C1\uC774 \uC788\uC5C8\uB294\uB370, \uADF8\uAC8C \uBC14\uB85C \uC800
      \uBC88\uAC1C\uC57C. "
    Text_EN: "Now, at the very edge of this forest's cliff, there was a magical phenomenon\u2014and
      that's exactly the lightning you see over there!"
    portrait1: 0
    direction1: 0
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 0
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 0
    BG: 20058
    CG: 0
