    GroupID: 3023
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "365\uC77C \uB0B4\uB0B4 \uBC88\uAC1C\uAC00 \uCE58\uB294 \uC2E0\uBE44\uD55C
      \uD604\uC0C1\uC774\uC9C0. "
    Text_EN: "It\u2019s a magical event where lightning strikes non-stop all year
