  - ID: 101051
    GroupID: 3026
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC131\uC778\uC2DD\uC740 \uCF54\uB77C\uC758 \uAD6C\uC5ED \uD14C\uB450\uB9AC\uC5D0\uC11C
      10\uBD84\uB9CC \uBC84\uD168\uB3C4 \uC778\uC815\uD574\uC918. "
    Text_EN: I mean, for the Cora' trials, they give you a pass even if you just
      hold out for ten minutes at the very edge of cora's territory!
