    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uAE30\uB85D! \uAE30\uB85D\uC744 \uBCF4\uACE0 \uC2F6\uC5B4. "
    Text_EN: The records! Oh, I just absolutely need to lay my eyes on the records!
