  - ID: 101127
    GroupID: 3029
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uC5D0\uD074\uB808"
    name_EN: Ecle
    Text_KR: "\uBB3C\uB860\uC774\uB2E4. \uCC98\uC74C\uC5D4 \uCF54\uB77C\uC758 \uBB38\uC81C\uB97C
      \uD574\uACB0\uD558\uAE30 \uC704\uD574 \uBD81\uC801\uC600\uC9C0\uB9CC, \uC9C0\uAE08\uC740..."
    Text_EN: Of course. At first, this place was crowded with people trying to fix
      Cora's issue. But now...
    portrait1: 0
    direction1: 0
    portrait2: 400021
    direction2: 1
    portrait3: 400070
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 3
    BG: 20065
    CG: 0
    BGM: 2010
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 101128
    GroupID: 3029
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uC5D0\uD074\uB808"
    name_EN: Ecle
    Text_KR: "\uC544\uBB34\uB3C4 \uC5C6\uB2E4."
    Text_EN: No one in here.
    portrait1: 0
    direction1: 0
    portrait2: 400020
    direction2: 1
    portrait3: 400070
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 3
    BG: 20065
    CG: 0
