    GroupID: 3029
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uCC45\uC740 \uC815\uB9D0 \uC88B\uC740 \uCE5C\uAD6C\uC9C0. "
    Text_EN: A good book is honestly the finest companion you could ask for!
