    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uBC94\uB78C \uC790\uCCB4 \uBCF4\uB2E4\uB294 \uBC94\uB78C\uC5D0 \uCE68\uC2DD\uB2F9\uD55C
      \uB204\uAD70\uAC00\uAC00 \uC9C0\uC6B0\uB294 \uC77C\uC774 \uB9CE\uC9C0!"
    Text_EN: "Honestly, it\u2019s rarely the Overflow itself that does the erasing.
      More often than not, it\u2019s someone already consumed by the Overflow who
      goes around wiping out the records!"
