    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC5D0\uD074\uB808\uAC00 \uB9D0\uD574\uC8FC\uAE38, \uBC88\uAC1C \uCE58\uB294
      \uD68D\uC218\uB294 2.1\uBC30, \uC138\uAE30\uB294 5\uBC30\uAC00 \uB298\uC5C8\uB294\uB370..."
    Text_EN: According to Ecle, the lightning strikes increased by 2.1 times, and
      the intensity shot up by 5 times...
    portrait1: 0
    direction1: 0
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 0
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 0
    BG: 20078
    CG: 0
    BGM: 2012
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 101283
    GroupID: 3033
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC5B4\uB5BB\uAC8C \uBC88\uAC1C\uB97C \uB9DE\uACE0 \uC8FD\uC740 \uC6A9\uC778\uC871\uC774
      \uD55C \uBA85\uB3C4 \uC5C6\uB294 \uAC78\uAE4C?"
    Text_EN: so how on earth is there not a single Dragonkin who died from getting
      struck? It just doesn't add up, you know!
    portrait1: 0
    direction1: 0
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 0
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 0
    BG: 20078
    CG: 0
    BGM: 2012
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 101284
    GroupID: 3033
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uD55C \uBC88\uC774\uB77C\uB3C4 \uB9DE\uACE0 \uBC84\uD2F0\uBA74 \uC218\uD638\uC790\uB85C
      \uC778\uC815\uD574\uC8FC\uB294 \uAC15\uD55C \uBC88\uAC1C\uC600\uB294\uB370
      \uB9D0\uC774\uC57C. "
    Text_EN: I mean, it was supposed to be this crazy powerful lightning where you're
      recognized as a Guardian if you can take just a single hit!
    portrait1: 0
    direction1: 0
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 0
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 0
    BG: 20078
    CG: 0
    BGM: 2012
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 101285
    GroupID: 3033
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uADF8\uB807\uB2E4\uBA74 \uAC04\uB2E8\uD558\uC9C0, \uD3C9\uC18C\uC758
      \uBC88\uAC1C\uC640, \uC131\uC778\uC2DD\uC758 \uB3C4\uC804\uC790\uAC00 \uB9DE\uB294
      \uBC88\uAC1C \uC218\uCE58\uAC00 \uB2EC\uB790\uB358\uAC70\uC57C. "
    Text_EN: "So, it\u2019s actually pretty simple\u2014the lightning levels for
      standard days and the ones the coming-of-age challengers got hit by were totally
      different, you know!"
    portrait1: 0
    direction1: 0
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 0
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 0
    BG: 20078
    CG: 0
    BGM: 2012
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 101286
    GroupID: 3033
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uC5B4\uB5A0\uD55C \uC774\uC720\uB85C \uC138\uAE30\uAC00 \uC870\uC808\uB418\uC5C8\uB2E4.'
      \uB77C\uACE0 \uC0DD\uAC01\uD574\uBCF4\uAE30\uB85C \uD588\uC9C0. "
    Text_EN: 'So, I decided to look at it this way: ''The intensity was actually
      being adjusted for some specific reason!'
    portrait1: 0
    direction1: 0
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 0
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 0
    BG: 20078
    CG: 0
    BGM: 2012
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 101287
    GroupID: 3033
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uB610, \uBD84\uBA85 \uBC88\uAC1C\uB97C \uB9DE\uACE0 \uC0B4\uC558\uB294\uB370
      \uC65C \uC218\uD638\uC790\uC758 \uAC01\uC131\uD558\uC9C0 \uC54A\uB294 \uAC78\uAE4C?"
    Text_EN: And they clearly survived getting struck by the lightning, so why on
      earth aren't they awakening as Guardians?
    portrait1: 0
    direction1: 0
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 0
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 0
    BG: 20078
    CG: 0
    BGM: 2012
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 101288
    GroupID: 3033
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uB798\uB9AC"
    name_EN: Rary
    Text_KR: "\uADF8\uAC74 \uADF8 \uBC88\uAC1C\uAC00 \uCF54\uB77C\uC758 \uBC88\uAC1C\uAC00
      \uC544\uB2C8\uC5C8\uAE30 \uB54C\uBB38\uC774\uC57C."
