    GroupID: 3049
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uD398\uC5B4"
    name_EN: Fair
    Text_KR: "\uC6A9\uC0AC\uB77C\uBA74, \uC6A9\uC744 \uBB34\uCC14\uB7EC\uC57C\uC9C0. "
    Text_EN: If they're a hero, they're supposed to defeat the dragon.
