    BGM: 2016
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 101947
    GroupID: 3049
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uD398\uC5B4"
    name_EN: Fair
    Text_KR: "\uACE0\uC791 \uADF8\uB807\uAC8C \uC9E7\uC740 \uC2DC\uAC04\uC744 \uB300\uD654\uD55C
      \uB098\uB97C \uC704\uD574 \uC6B8\uC0C1\uC778 \uD45C\uC815\uC744 \uC9D3\uB2E4\uB2C8."
    Text_EN: To think you'd pull a face like that for someone you've only talked
      to for such a short time.
    portrait1: 400012
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
    direction2: 0
    portrait3: 400092
    direction3: 0
    speaker: 3
    BG: 20117
    CG: 0
    BGM: 2016
    SFX: 0
  - ID: 101948
    GroupID: 3049
    TextBox: 1
    name_KR: "\uD398\uC5B4"
    name_EN: Fair
    Text_KR: "\uC6A9\uC758 \uC81C\uC790\uAC00 \uC774\uB807\uAC8C \uAC10\uC815\uC801\uC774\uBA74
      \uC4F0\uB098."
    Text_EN: To think a dragon's disciple could be this emotional.
    portrait1: 400012
    direction1: 1
    portrait2: 0
